content: I've actually been experimenting with different cooking methods lately, and I've been trying to cook at least once a week, usually on Sundays. Last Sunday, I made that delicious chicken fajita recipe I mentioned earlier, and it was a hit! I've also been meal prepping on the weekends, making a big batch of rice and lentils that I can use throughout the week. It's been really convenient and has saved me money on food delivery.
